---
---

<section id="take-action">
  <div class="hero-bg">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <span class="section-label">Next step</span>
      <h2>Here&rsquo;s how you can help</h2>
      <p class="lede">
        A cleaner sky won&rsquo;t build itself. Pick an action below.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="content">
    <div class="action-panel">
      <div class="panel-icon">
        <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E0760E" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <circle cx="18" cy="5" r="3"/>
          <circle cx="6" cy="12" r="3"/>
          <circle cx="18" cy="19" r="3"/>
          <line x1="8.59" y1="13.51" x2="15.42" y2="17.49"/>
          <line x1="15.41" y1="6.51" x2="8.59" y2="10.49"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div class="panel-body">
        <h3>Share the plan</h3>
        <p>Send this site to your flying club, your airport manager, or your airline&rsquo;s sustainability team. The more people who see it, the harder it is to ignore.</p>
        <button class="action-btn" onclick="alert('Share functionality coming soon! For now, copy the URL and share it manually.')">
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <circle cx="18" cy="5" r="3"/>
            <circle cx="6" cy="12" r="3"/>
            <circle cx="18" cy="19" r="3"/>
            <line x1="8.59" y1="13.51" x2="15.42" y2="17.49"/>
            <line x1="15.41" y1="6.51" x2="8.59" y2="10.49"/>
          </svg>
          Share the Green Flight Plan
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="action-panel">
      <div class="panel-icon">
        <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E0760E" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <path d="M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z"/>
          <polyline points="22,6 12,13 2,6"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div class="panel-body">
        <script src='https://actionnetwork.org/widgets/v6/form/sign-up-for-updates-252?format=js&source=widget' is:inline></script><div id='can-form-area-sign-up-for-updates-252' style='width: 100%'><!-- this div is the target for our HTML insertion --></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="action-panel">
      <div class="panel-icon">
        <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E0760E" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <path d="M12 20h9"/>
          <path d="M16.5 3.5a2.121 2.121 0 0 1 3 3L7 19l-4 1 1-4L16.5 3.5z"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div class="panel-body">
        <h3>Write your representatives</h3>
        <p>Draft a message to your representative and senators urging them to sponsor a leaded-fuel phase-out bill and support electric-aviation infrastructure funding.</p>
        <button class="action-btn" onclick="alert('Letter-writing tool coming soon!')">
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M12 20h9"/>
            <path d="M16.5 3.5a2.121 2.121 0 0 1 3 3L7 19l-4 1 1-4L16.5 3.5z"/>
          </svg>
          Find your rep
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  section { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; }

  .hero-bg {
    width: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3D2400 0%, #7A4A0A 40%, #E0A020 100%);
    color: #fff;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 4rem 1.25rem;
  }

  .hero-content { max-width: 720px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.75rem; }

  .section-label {
    font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em; opacity: 0.6;
  }

  .hero-content h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin: 0; line-height: 1.15;
  }

  .hero-content .lede {
    font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.65; margin: 0; opacity: 0.9; max-width: 500px;
  }

  .content {
    max-width: 680px; display: flex; flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.25rem; padding: 4rem 1.25rem;
  }

  .action-panel {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--neutral-200);
    border-radius: 12px;
    background: #FAFAFA;
  }

  .panel-icon {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    background: #FFF5E6;
    border-radius: 12px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .panel-body {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    flex: 1;
  }

  .panel-body h3 {
    font-size: 1.125rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--neutral-900);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .panel-body p {
    font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.5; color: var(--neutral-500);
    margin: 0; max-width: 480px;
  }

  .action-btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.4rem;
    padding: 0.6rem 1.2rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #E0760E, #C0650A);
    color: #fff;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: transform 0.12s, box-shadow 0.12s;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(192, 101, 10, 0.25);
    align-self: flex-start;
  }

  .action-btn:hover {
    transform: translateY(-1px);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(192, 101, 10, 0.35);
  }

  .action-btn:active {
    transform: translateY(0);
  }

  .callout {
    display: flex; gap: 0.75rem; align-items: flex-start;
    padding: 1rem 1.25rem; background: #FFF5E6; border: 1px solid #FFD699;
    border-radius: 10px; font-size: 0.9375rem; line-height: 1.5; color: #7A3A00;
  }

  .callout svg { flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px; }
</style>
